# Next.js App Router

- Route groups: `(marketing)` and `(app)`
- Server components by default; client components only when necessary
- Default runtime nodejs; edge only via ADR
- Routes in `src/app/(app)/*` import UI from `src/features/*`
- No duplicated UI in `/app`
- Route handlers: `src/app/api/**/route.ts` for API endpoints
- Server actions preferred over client mutations
- Use Next.js metadata API for SEO
- Use Next.js Image component for images
